==Korean==

===Etymology===

From [[짧은]] (''jjalp.eun'', adjective form of [[짧다]], "to be short") + [[부리]] (''buri'', "beak") + [[참돌고래]] (''chamdolgorae'', "true dolphin")

===Noun===

'''짧은부리참돌고래''' (jjalp.eun.bu.ri.cham.dol.go.rae)

#  The [[short-beaked common dolphin]], ''[[Delphinus delphis]]''.

